==Описание==

The {{Button|[[File:Spreadsheet_AlignRight.svg|16px]] [[Spreadsheet_AlignRight|Spreadsheet AlignRight]]}} tool makes the text inside the cell align to the right.

==Применение==

# Make sure there is an active {{Button|[[File:Spreadsheet_CreateSheet.svg|16px]] [[Spreadsheet_CreateSheet|Spreadsheet]]}} open so that the button is enabled.
# Select a cell.
# Press the {{Button|[[File:Spreadsheet_AlignRight.svg|16px]] [[Spreadsheet_AlignRight|Spreadsheet AlignRight]]}} button.


